<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN:
    <li>questDescription->[asker_nameFull], a [asker_royalTitleInCurrentFaction] of [asker_faction_name] is calling from nearby. [asker_possessive] guards were killed in an ambush. [asker_pronoun] escaped, but is now being followed by (*Threat)a manhunting [animalKindDef_label](/Threat).\n\n[asker_nameDef] wants you to keep [asker_objective] safe at [map_definite] for a few hours until [asker_possessive] shuttle can come pick [asker_objective] up.\n\n[asker_pronoun] will bestow [royalFavorReward] [asker_faction_royalFavorLabel] on whoever accepts this quest. This is enough [asker_faction_royalFavorLabel] to receive the royal title of Novice, and all benefits that come with it - including the first level of psychic powers.</li>
  -->
  <Intro_Wimp.questDescriptionRules.rulesStrings>
    <li>questDescription->[asker_nameFull]، [asker_royalTitleInCurrentFaction] من [asker_faction_name] يتصل من مكان قريب. قُتل حراسـ[asker_possessive] في كمين. نجا [asker_pronoun]، لكن الآن يطارده (*Threat)[animalKindDef_label] مفترس(/Threat).\n\nيريد [asker_nameDef] منك الحفاظ على سلامةـ[asker_objective] في [map_definite] لبضع ساعات حتى يتمكن مكوكـ[asker_possessive] من القدوم لاصطحابـ[asker_objective].\n\nسيمنح [asker_pronoun] [royalFavorReward] [asker_faction_royalFavorLabel] لمن يقبل هذه المهمة. وهذا يكفي من [asker_faction_royalFavorLabel] للحصول على اللقب الملكي 'مبتدئ'، وجميع المزايا التي تأتي معه - بما في ذلك المستوى الأول من القوى النفسية.</li>
 </Intro_Wimp.questDescriptionRules.rulesStrings>
  <!-- EN:
    <li>questName->the [adjAny] [asker_royalTitleInCurrentFaction]</li>
    <li>adjAny->hunted</li>
    <li>adjAny->fleeing</li>
    <li>adjAny->solitary</li>
    <li>adjAny->ambushed</li>
  -->
  <Intro_Wimp.questNameRules.rulesStrings>
    <li>questName->[asker_royalTitleInCurrentFaction] الـ[adjAny]</li>
    <li>adjAny->مطارَد</li>
    <li>adjAny->هارب</li>
    <li>adjAny->وحيد</li>
    <li>adjAny->متربص</li>
 </Intro_Wimp.questNameRules.rulesStrings>
  <!-- EN: [animalKindDef_label] arrived -->
  <Intro_Wimp.LetterLabelAnimalArrived.slateRef>وصل [animalKindDef_label]</Intro_Wimp.LetterLabelAnimalArrived.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: The [animalKindDef_label] that [asker_nameDef] was fleeing has arrived.\n\nIt turned out to be quite gentle and not aggressive at all. -->
  <Intro_Wimp.LetterTextAnimalArrived.slateRef>وصل [animalKindDef_label] الذي كان يهرب منه [asker_nameDef].\n\nتبين أنه وديع للغاية وغير عدواني على الإطلاق.</Intro_Wimp.LetterTextAnimalArrived.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: Manhunting [animalKindDef_label] -->
  <Intro_Wimp.LetterLabelAngryAnimal.slateRef>[animalKindDef_label] مفترس</Intro_Wimp.LetterLabelAngryAnimal.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: The [animalKindDef_label] which was following [asker_nameFull] has arrived in the area. -->
  <Intro_Wimp.LetterTextAngryAnimal.slateRef>وصل [animalKindDef_label] الذي كان يتبع [asker_nameFull] إلى المنطقة.</Intro_Wimp.LetterTextAngryAnimal.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: Should depart on shuttle -->
  <Intro_Wimp.InspectStringDepartShuttle.slateRef>يجب المغادرة بالمكوك</Intro_Wimp.InspectStringDepartShuttle.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: Shuttle arrived -->
  <Intro_Wimp.LetterLabelShuttleArrived.slateRef>وصول المكوك</Intro_Wimp.LetterLabelShuttleArrived.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: The shuttle has arrived to collect [asker_nameDef]. -->
  <Intro_Wimp.LetterTextShuttleArrived.slateRef>وصل المكوك لاصطحاب [asker_nameDef].</Intro_Wimp.LetterTextShuttleArrived.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: Guest died: {SUBJECT_definite} -->
  <Intro_Wimp.LetterLabelGuestDied.slateRef>توفي الضيف: {SUBJECT_definite}</Intro_Wimp.LetterLabelGuestDied.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: {SUBJECT_definite}, who you were charged to protect, has died. [failLetterEndingCommon] -->
  <Intro_Wimp.LetterTextGuestDied.slateRef>{SUBJECT_definite}، الذي كُنت مكلفًا بحمايته، قد توفي. [failLetterEndingCommon]</Intro_Wimp.LetterTextGuestDied.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: Guest left behind: {SUBJECT_definite} -->
  <Intro_Wimp.root.nodes.askerLeftBehind.node.nodes.Letter.label.slateRef>ضيف متروك: {SUBJECT_definite}</Intro_Wimp.root.nodes.askerLeftBehind.node.nodes.Letter.label.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: {SUBJECT_definite}, who you were charged to protect, has been left behind. [failLetterEndingCommon] -->
  <Intro_Wimp.root.nodes.askerLeftBehind.node.nodes.Letter.text.slateRef>{SUBJECT_definite}، الذي كُنت مكلفًا بحمايته، قد تُرك. [failLetterEndingCommon]</Intro_Wimp.root.nodes.askerLeftBehind.node.nodes.Letter.text.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: Unauthorized surgery: {SUBJECT_definite} -->
  <Intro_Wimp.LetterLabelUnauthorizedSurgery.slateRef>جراحة غير مصرح بها: {SUBJECT_definite}</Intro_Wimp.LetterLabelUnauthorizedSurgery.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: Unauthorized, violating surgery has been performed on {SUBJECT_definite}, who you were charged to protect. Because of this violation, [asker_pronoun] will now attempt to leave. [failLetterEndingCommon] -->
  <Intro_Wimp.LetterTextUnauthorizedSurgery.slateRef>أُجريت جراحة غير مصرح بها ومخالفة على {SUBJECT_definite}، الذي كُنت مكلفًا بحمايته. بسبب هذا الانتهاك، سيحاول [asker_pronoun] الآن المغادرة. [failLetterEndingCommon]</Intro_Wimp.LetterTextUnauthorizedSurgery.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: Xenogerm absorbed: {SUBJECT_definite} -->
  <Intro_Wimp.root.nodes.askerXenogermAbsorbed.node.nodes.Letter.label.slateRef>امتصاص زينوجيرم: {SUBJECT_definite}</Intro_Wimp.root.nodes.askerXenogermAbsorbed.node.nodes.Letter.label.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: {SUBJECT_definite}, who you were charged to protect, has had {SUBJECT_possessive} xenogerm forcibly absorbed. Because of this violation, {SUBJECT_pronoun} will now attempt to leave. [failLetterEndingCommon] -->
  <Intro_Wimp.root.nodes.askerXenogermAbsorbed.node.nodes.Letter.text.slateRef>{SUBJECT_definite}، الذي كُنت مكلفًا بحمايته، تم امتصاص زينوجيرمـ{SUBJECT_possessive} بالقوة. بسبب هذا الانتهاك، سيحاول {SUBJECT_pronoun} الآن المغادرة. [failLetterEndingCommon]</Intro_Wimp.root.nodes.askerXenogermAbsorbed.node.nodes.Letter.text.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: Captured: {SUBJECT_definite} -->
  <Intro_Wimp.LetterLabelCaptured.slateRef>أُسر: {SUBJECT_definite}</Intro_Wimp.LetterLabelCaptured.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: {SUBJECT_definite}, who you were charged to host, has been arrested. [failLetterEndingCommon] -->
  <Intro_Wimp.LetterTextCaptured.slateRef>تم القبض على {SUBJECT_definite}، الذي كُنت مكلفًا باستضافته. [failLetterEndingCommon]</Intro_Wimp.LetterTextCaptured.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: Guest lost: {SUBJECT_definite} -->
  <Intro_Wimp.LetterLabelGuestLost.slateRef>فُقد الضيف: {SUBJECT_definite}</Intro_Wimp.LetterLabelGuestLost.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: {SUBJECT_definite}, who you were charged to protect, has left the designated settlement. [failLetterEndingCommon] -->
  <Intro_Wimp.LetterTextGuestLost.slateRef>{SUBJECT_definite}، الذي كُنت مكلفًا بحمايته، قد غادر المستوطنة المحددة. [failLetterEndingCommon]</Intro_Wimp.LetterTextGuestLost.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: Guest lost: {SUBJECT_definite} -->
  <Intro_Wimp.LetterLabelLodgerRanWild.slateRef>فُقد الضيف: {SUBJECT_definite}</Intro_Wimp.LetterLabelLodgerRanWild.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: {SUBJECT_definite}, who you were charged to protect, has run wild. [failLetterEndingCommon] -->
  <Intro_Wimp.LetterTextLodgerRanWild.slateRef>{SUBJECT_definite}، الذي كُنت مكلفًا بحمايته، قد توحش. [failLetterEndingCommon]</Intro_Wimp.LetterTextLodgerRanWild.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: Shuttle destroyed -->
  <Intro_Wimp.LetterLabelShuttleDestroyed.slateRef>تدمير المكوك</Intro_Wimp.LetterLabelShuttleDestroyed.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: The shuttle sent to collect [asker_nameDef] has been destroyed. [asker_pronoun] will now leave on foot. [failLetterEndingCommon] -->
  <Intro_Wimp.LetterTextShuttleDestroyed.slateRef>المكوك الذي أُرسل لاصطحاب [asker_nameDef] قد دُمّر. سيغادر [asker_pronoun] الآن سيرًا على الأقدام. [failLetterEndingCommon]</Intro_Wimp.LetterTextShuttleDestroyed.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: Shuttle left behind -->
  <Intro_Wimp.root.nodes.pickupShipThingLeftBehind.node.nodes.Letter.label.slateRef>مكوك متروك</Intro_Wimp.root.nodes.pickupShipThingLeftBehind.node.nodes.Letter.label.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: The shuttle sent to collect [asker_nameDef] has been left behind. [asker_pronoun] will now leave on foot. -->
  <Intro_Wimp.root.nodes.pickupShipThingLeftBehind.node.nodes.Letter.text.slateRef>المكوك الذي أُرسل لاصطحاب [asker_nameDef] قد تُرك. سيغادر [asker_pronoun] الآن سيرًا على الأقدام.</Intro_Wimp.root.nodes.pickupShipThingLeftBehind.node.nodes.Letter.text.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: Quest failed: [resolvedQuestName] -->
  <Intro_Wimp.LetterLabelQuestFailed.slateRef>فشل المهمة: [resolvedQuestName]</Intro_Wimp.LetterLabelQuestFailed.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: The shuttle sent to collect [asker_nameDef] has departed without [asker_objective]. [asker_pronoun] will now leave on foot. [failLetterEndingCommon] -->
  <Intro_Wimp.LetterTextQuestFailed.slateRef>المكوك الذي أُرسل لاصطحاب [asker_nameDef] قد غادر بدونـ[asker_objective]. سيغادر [asker_pronoun] الآن سيرًا على الأقدام. [failLetterEndingCommon]</Intro_Wimp.LetterTextQuestFailed.slateRef>
  
</LanguageData>
